Intracellular Ca(2+) and K(+) concentration in Brassica oleracea leaf induces 
differential expression of transporter and stress-related genes.

Lee J(1), Kim J(2), Choi JP(3), Lee M(4), Kim MK(5), Lee YH(6), Hur Y(7), Nou 
IS(8), Park SU(9), Min SR(10), Kim H(11)(12).

Author information:
(1)Korea Research Institute of Bioscience and Biotechnology, 125 Gwahangno, 
Yuseong-gu, Daejeon, 305-806, Republic of Korea. leejy@kribb.re.kr.
(2)Korea Research Institute of Bioscience and Biotechnology, 125 Gwahangno, 
